WEBVTT

00:00:02.080 --> 00:00:08.960
Hi, my name is Brandon, and I have had

00:00:06.799 --> 00:00:10.639
an experience with the Lord that he

00:00:08.960 --> 00:00:12.880
keeps telling me I need to tell

00:00:10.639 --> 00:00:15.759
people about. I've never really

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:18.640
talked in front of a camera before

00:00:15.759 --> 00:00:22.960
like this, but he wanted me to

00:00:18.640 --> 00:00:25.359
document it and tell everybody

00:00:22.960 --> 00:00:27.920
what happened and what kind of

00:00:25.359 --> 00:00:32.200
experience I had with him. This

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:34.719
experience lasted all night long, and

00:00:32.200 --> 00:00:37.520
I'm just asking the Holy Spirit right

00:00:34.719 --> 00:00:40.640
now to help me communicate

00:00:37.520 --> 00:00:43.360
everything that I saw.

00:00:40.640 --> 00:00:45.840
It's really important because

00:00:43.360 --> 00:00:49.079
Jesus Christ is coming, and he told me

00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:53.440
he's coming face to face.

00:00:49.079 --> 00:00:55.800
This experience happened on July

00:00:53.440 --> 00:00:59.199
6th,

00:00:55.800 --> 00:01:01.199
2014, and I've held it all these

00:00:59.199 --> 00:01:03.039
years. I wrote it down on paper and

00:01:01.199 --> 00:01:06.640
released it to some people on Facebook

00:01:03.039 --> 00:01:07.260
and to some church friends and family.

00:01:08.520 --> 00:01:16.158
Some people received it and some

00:01:12.560 --> 00:01:18.479
people didn't. I'm just a

00:01:16.159 --> 00:01:24.600
deliverer of the message that he gave

00:01:18.479 --> 00:01:28.680
me. I'm not here to argue about

00:01:24.600 --> 00:01:32.240
theology or

00:01:28.680 --> 00:01:34.640
try to convince anybody of my

00:01:32.240 --> 00:01:37.640
experience. I'm going to tell you

00:01:34.640 --> 00:01:41.200
exactly what happened, exactly how it

00:01:37.640 --> 00:01:43.159
happened, from the beginning to

00:01:41.200 --> 00:01:46.240
the end.

00:01:43.159 --> 00:01:51.240
I don't know if you're a mid-tribulation, post-tribulation,

00:01:46.240 --> 00:01:54.720
or pre-tribulation believer.

00:01:54.920 --> 00:02:00.880
Like I said, I'm not here

00:01:57.640 --> 00:02:03.280
to argue or try to get you to say

00:02:00.880 --> 00:02:06.158
anything in the comments about

00:02:03.280 --> 00:02:10.080
what I saw or what I experienced.

00:02:06.159 --> 00:02:12.200
I'm just telling you what I saw and

00:02:10.080 --> 00:02:16.640
we'll go from there.

00:02:12.200 --> 00:02:20.000
It all started out while I was asleep;

00:02:16.640 --> 00:02:22.000
I went to bed a normal night,

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:24.640
nothing different. I went to sleep

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:27.360
and in the middle of my sleep, all of

00:02:24.640 --> 00:02:30.480
a sudden, I don't know if I was in

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:33.519
my body or out of my body. I don't

00:02:30.480 --> 00:02:36.000
know how it happened; all I

00:02:33.519 --> 00:02:39.599
know is all of a sudden I was standing

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:42.879
with Jesus, and he was on my right

00:02:39.599 --> 00:02:46.599
hand the whole time in this experience.

00:02:42.879 --> 00:02:51.920
He grabbed a hold of my hand and

00:02:46.599 --> 00:02:55.760
I'll go from there. The first

00:02:51.920 --> 00:02:57.760
scene, per se, of what I saw

00:02:55.760 --> 00:03:00.399
was Jesus standing on my right

00:02:57.760 --> 00:03:03.359
hand. He had a hold of my hand and we

00:03:00.400 --> 00:03:05.920
were in a town. I don't know what town

00:03:03.360 --> 00:03:08.720
we were in, but I know that there was a big

00:03:05.920 --> 00:03:12.319
white building over to the

00:03:08.720 --> 00:03:14.720
side. I was looking up

00:03:12.319 --> 00:03:17.359
at this big white building and

00:03:14.720 --> 00:03:20.480
at the sky, and the

00:03:17.360 --> 00:03:23.680
sky was alive. It was like it was

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:26.959
moving; it was full

00:03:23.680 --> 00:03:31.599
of lightning and very spooky

00:03:26.959 --> 00:03:33.920
looking. I looked out over the

00:03:31.599 --> 00:03:37.440
horizon and there was this

00:03:33.920 --> 00:03:39.679
lady running towards me, and she started

00:03:37.440 --> 00:03:41.680
screaming. They were all screaming

00:03:39.680 --> 00:03:44.879
in terror; they were all freaking out.

00:03:41.680 --> 00:03:48.720
It was incredible.

00:03:44.879 --> 00:03:51.760
They were saying, "They're gone.

00:03:48.720 --> 00:03:53.440
They're gone."I said, "Who's gone?"I

00:03:51.760 --> 00:03:56.798
told this lady,

00:03:53.440 --> 00:03:59.040
"Who's gone?"and she said, "Did you

00:03:56.799 --> 00:04:00.720
not see?"I said, "Did I not see

00:03:59.040 --> 00:04:02.879
what, ma'am? What are you

00:04:00.720 --> 00:04:05.680
talking about?"At this

00:04:02.879 --> 00:04:07.518
time, she could see me. Now, not every

00:04:05.680 --> 00:04:10.560
time in

00:04:07.519 --> 00:04:13.360
this experience were

00:04:10.560 --> 00:04:16.399
people able to see me.

00:04:13.360 --> 00:04:19.519
In this instance, she could

00:04:16.399 --> 00:04:22.400
not see Jesus, but she could see me.

00:04:19.519 --> 00:04:25.080
She said, "The aliens? The

00:04:22.400 --> 00:04:28.479
aliens came and got the Christians."I

00:04:25.080 --> 00:04:30.240
said, "The aliens?"She

00:04:28.479 --> 00:04:33.080
said, "Yes, they all

00:04:30.240 --> 00:04:37.280
disappeared. They went up."At

00:04:33.080 --> 00:04:39.120
that moment, she just ran off.

00:04:37.280 --> 00:04:41.599
She was frantic, screaming in terror. She

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:43.479
ran as

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:46.720
fast as she could,

00:04:43.479 --> 00:04:49.199
panicking. I looked out over the

00:04:46.720 --> 00:04:51.639
horizon of the city. I was up on a

00:04:49.199 --> 00:04:55.040
hill at this time and I could see

00:04:51.639 --> 00:04:57.919
everything on fire. Everything was on fire—the

00:04:55.040 --> 00:05:02.560
cars, the houses, the

00:04:57.919 --> 00:05:04.719
buildings. It was like

00:05:02.560 --> 00:05:07.600
chaos beyond anything you could ever

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:10.560
comprehend was happening at this time.

00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:12.479
You could smell the smoke.

00:05:10.560 --> 00:05:14.160
People were looting; they were stealing

00:05:12.479 --> 00:05:15.520
out of cars and

00:05:14.160 --> 00:05:18.320
buildings. They were

00:05:15.520 --> 00:05:22.400
trashing the city

00:05:18.320 --> 00:05:26.080
where I was. Jesus didn't

00:05:22.400 --> 00:05:28.799
say anything. In fact, he never spoke;

00:05:26.080 --> 00:05:31.440
I could perceive his thoughts when he

00:05:28.800 --> 00:05:33.919
was touching my hand. I knew what he was

00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:36.800
thinking, but he never said anything out

00:05:33.919 --> 00:05:39.359
of his mouth. He could understand what I

00:05:36.800 --> 00:05:41.919
was thinking, but I never said anything to

00:05:39.360 --> 00:05:44.400
him.

00:05:41.919 --> 00:05:47.440
I was just looking across the city, thinking,

00:05:44.400 --> 00:05:51.919
"Oh my gosh, what is going on?"All

00:05:47.440 --> 00:05:55.440
of a sudden, we translated. We

00:05:51.919 --> 00:05:58.320
left that spot and went to

00:05:55.440 --> 00:06:00.000
another spot. He grabbed my hand—we

00:05:58.320 --> 00:06:02.560
were still holding hands—but it was like

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:04.840
we just

00:06:02.560 --> 00:06:08.680
disappeared and came to another

00:06:04.840 --> 00:06:10.679
time. In this time frame, I

00:06:08.680 --> 00:06:14.000
was

00:06:10.680 --> 00:06:15.520
looking over Europe. I knew I was

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:17.600
looking over Europe because I was

00:06:15.520 --> 00:06:20.000
standing back, like I was watching a

00:06:17.600 --> 00:06:23.039
movie. It was very strange. I

00:06:20.000 --> 00:06:24.520
was looking out over Europe and

00:06:23.039 --> 00:06:29.280
I saw this

00:06:24.520 --> 00:06:32.318
man in Berlin. All the

00:06:29.280 --> 00:06:34.880
world leaders were behind a table. It

00:06:32.319 --> 00:06:38.400
was a round table in Berlin. It

00:06:34.880 --> 00:06:40.400
looked like a big office. It was a

00:06:38.400 --> 00:06:42.960
brown table, and there were

00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:45.840
chairs all around it. All of these

00:06:42.960 --> 00:06:49.758
world leaders were

00:06:45.840 --> 00:06:51.919
behind this big table,

00:06:49.759 --> 00:06:54.880
and this man—I didn't know who he

00:06:51.919 --> 00:06:57.758
was at the time, but

00:06:54.880 --> 00:07:02.000
I'll tell you later—and all of the

00:06:57.759 --> 00:07:04.160
people were asking him for help.

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:06.400
They were asking him for a solution to

00:07:04.160 --> 00:07:10.880
all the rioting and the craziness

00:07:06.400 --> 00:07:14.239
that was going on. He was

00:07:10.880 --> 00:07:18.159
instructing them on what to do. He had

00:07:14.240 --> 00:07:20.800
all the wisdom and was very

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:24.800
powerful in demeanor, the way he carried

00:07:20.800 --> 00:07:27.520
himself. He was wearing a gray suit,

00:07:24.800 --> 00:07:32.639
and he was a Middle Eastern

00:07:27.520 --> 00:07:37.280
man. All of a sudden, that

00:07:32.639 --> 00:07:39.919
scene was over, but the

00:07:37.280 --> 00:07:42.559
Lord at that time spoke to me about a

00:07:39.919 --> 00:07:44.960
scripture and showed me

00:07:42.560 --> 00:07:48.160
how everyone would give over their

00:07:44.960 --> 00:07:50.198
kingdoms to him within one hour. As

00:07:48.160 --> 00:07:53.680
I said, I'm not a Bible

00:07:50.199 --> 00:07:56.800
scholar or a theology major;

00:07:53.680 --> 00:07:59.280
I'm just a guy who loves Jesus

00:07:56.800 --> 00:08:01.360
and seeks Him with all my

00:07:59.280 --> 00:08:04.440
heart, and I had this experience with

00:08:01.360 --> 00:08:09.360
Him.

00:08:04.440 --> 00:08:13.440
The next scene I see is this man

00:08:09.360 --> 00:08:17.440
on TV—he's on

00:08:13.440 --> 00:08:20.560
CNN, Fox, and everywhere.

00:08:17.440 --> 00:08:24.240
He is telling all the people

00:08:20.560 --> 00:08:26.720
of the world what happened to the

00:08:24.240 --> 00:08:31.599
people who disappeared,

00:08:26.720 --> 00:08:34.080
explaining

00:08:31.599 --> 00:08:36.760
that they were rebellious, that

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:39.120
they were taken away out of

00:08:36.760 --> 00:08:41.039
rebellion, and that they were being

00:08:39.120 --> 00:08:43.200
punished. All these people were punished—it

00:08:41.039 --> 00:08:44.800
was the Christians, and they

00:08:43.200 --> 00:08:47.440
were all being

00:08:44.800 --> 00:08:49.279
taken out. Then he explained

00:08:47.440 --> 00:08:54.000
that he was the new leader of

00:08:49.279 --> 00:08:56.600
the world. I looked out and

00:08:54.000 --> 00:08:59.360
saw

00:08:59.360 --> 00:09:05.279
how he was gradually taking power. I want to tell

00:09:02.160 --> 00:09:07.439
you

00:09:05.279 --> 00:09:10.080
what I

00:09:07.440 --> 00:09:12.360
felt;

00:09:10.080 --> 00:09:14.959
this is very

00:09:12.360 --> 00:09:17.640
important: everybody wakes up every

00:09:14.959 --> 00:09:21.000
single day with a peace

00:09:17.640 --> 00:09:24.399
they don't realize they

00:09:21.000 --> 00:09:26.399
have. They go to bed with it and

00:09:24.399 --> 00:09:30.880
wake up with it. Even the worst

00:09:26.399 --> 00:09:32.640
sinner in the world has a form of

00:09:30.880 --> 00:09:33.560
peace inside of them that they don't

00:09:32.640 --> 00:09:37.240
even

00:09:33.560 --> 00:09:40.359
realize. When the rapture

00:09:37.240 --> 00:09:45.600
happens and we're taken

00:09:40.360 --> 00:09:49.920
out, there is a void of peace like

00:09:45.600 --> 00:09:52.839
I've never felt in all of my life;

00:09:49.920 --> 00:09:55.599
it blankets the

00:09:52.839 --> 00:09:59.120
earth. I used to think that the Holy

00:09:55.600 --> 00:10:00.959
Spirit left with us because He dwells in

00:09:59.120 --> 00:10:03.600
each Christian. He dwells in us, and

00:10:00.959 --> 00:10:06.000
when we invite him into our heart,

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:08.640
I believe that he went with us when

00:10:06.000 --> 00:10:11.000
the rapture happened. I cannot

00:10:08.640 --> 00:10:15.279
back that up biblically. I don't

00:10:11.000 --> 00:10:19.160
know. All I know is that there is no

00:10:15.279 --> 00:10:22.560
prayer covering, there is no sense of

00:10:19.160 --> 00:10:24.279
peace, there is no joy. It is

00:10:22.560 --> 00:10:27.319
absolute

00:10:24.279 --> 00:10:31.600
chaos. And this

00:10:27.320 --> 00:10:34.399
man has a sense that whenever everybody

00:10:31.600 --> 00:10:36.519
looks at him, when everybody is

00:10:34.399 --> 00:10:40.320
gazing upon

00:10:36.519 --> 00:10:43.600
him, a false sense of peace is what I

00:10:40.320 --> 00:10:46.720
want to say. He

00:10:43.600 --> 00:10:50.959
brings a peace when he is on the TV. He

00:10:46.720 --> 00:10:53.440
brings a sense of comfort that

00:10:50.959 --> 00:10:54.880
everybody wants to follow him so quickly

00:10:53.440 --> 00:10:57.839
because they are so scared and everybody is

00:10:54.880 --> 00:11:01.279
so tormented. They all turn

00:10:57.839 --> 00:11:04.000
to him so quickly out of that peace that

00:11:01.279 --> 00:11:06.600
he brings, but it is dirty.

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:10.560
I don't know how to describe

00:11:06.600 --> 00:11:13.839
it. So he is on the TV, and he is

00:11:10.560 --> 00:11:17.880
telling everybody what happened to

00:11:13.839 --> 00:11:20.040
the Christians. Then I see

00:11:17.880 --> 00:11:23.680
people in the

00:11:20.040 --> 00:11:26.279
Iran and Iraq area over there—Pakistan,

00:11:23.680 --> 00:11:29.839
that area over there—they were

00:11:26.279 --> 00:11:33.920
rejoicing. And they were all calling out

00:11:29.839 --> 00:11:36.320
and saying the Mahdi has come. The Mahdi

00:11:33.920 --> 00:11:39.439
has come. And I don't know what

00:11:36.320 --> 00:11:42.720
that means. I have studied it

00:11:39.440 --> 00:11:44.240
now a little bit more. I

00:11:42.720 --> 00:11:47.040
don't know what I'm allowed

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:49.600
to say about all this as

00:11:47.040 --> 00:11:51.680
far as on YouTube and what will be

00:11:49.600 --> 00:11:54.880
allowed. I don't want my video to get

00:11:51.680 --> 00:11:56.680
flagged, but they were calling it the Mahdi.

00:11:54.880 --> 00:11:59.360
They were calling him the Mahdi.

00:11:56.680 --> 00:12:03.279
And so everybody was calling

00:11:59.360 --> 00:12:06.639
him the Mahdi. And so he was himself

00:12:03.279 --> 00:12:10.240
Middle Eastern. He was a Muslim. I

00:12:06.639 --> 00:12:14.480
know this because he said he was and he

00:12:10.240 --> 00:12:17.279
had a... Okay, I won't get

00:12:14.480 --> 00:12:22.800
to that part yet. Okay, this is what

00:12:17.279 --> 00:12:25.600
happens next. I see him come on TV,

00:12:22.800 --> 00:12:28.560
and he is telling everybody to bring

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:30.880
their Bibles into the stadiums, into

00:12:28.560 --> 00:12:33.599
these areas. He said, 'If you see a

00:12:30.880 --> 00:12:36.480
Bible, it is mandated by law that

00:12:33.600 --> 00:12:40.360
everybody brings these Bibles into these areas.'And

00:12:36.480 --> 00:12:42.959
so, it was like courthouses,

00:12:40.360 --> 00:12:45.560
places like that. They were

00:12:42.959 --> 00:12:49.199
all like police stations, things like

00:12:45.560 --> 00:12:52.880
that. He brings these Bibles in and they

00:12:49.200 --> 00:12:54.720
start stacking them up—big

00:12:52.880 --> 00:12:57.360
shelves full. There were thousands,

00:12:54.720 --> 00:12:59.839
millions of Bibles just everywhere. And

00:12:57.360 --> 00:13:01.519
everybody just willfully

00:12:59.839 --> 00:13:03.360
did it; they just brought

00:13:01.519 --> 00:13:04.639
in the Bibles. And I remember seeing

00:13:03.360 --> 00:13:07.600
them everywhere. There were stacks and

00:13:04.639 --> 00:13:10.560
stacks of Bibles everywhere. And so they

00:13:07.600 --> 00:13:12.720
would write down your name on a piece of

00:13:10.560 --> 00:13:14.719
paper of who brought the Bible and what

00:13:12.720 --> 00:13:17.440
it was or whatever. And he told

00:13:14.720 --> 00:13:19.200
everybody, 'If you want to come and

00:13:17.440 --> 00:13:22.160
check out the Bible and look at it, it is okay.'We'll

00:13:19.200 --> 00:13:24.399
let you. It was kind of

00:13:22.160 --> 00:13:28.079
a trick, though, because whenever

00:13:24.399 --> 00:13:30.079
people came in and wrote on

00:13:28.079 --> 00:13:31.760
the paper to check out their Bible that they brought in—if they wanted to look at it

00:13:30.079 --> 00:13:34.719
again—you

00:13:31.760 --> 00:13:38.560
were

00:13:34.720 --> 00:13:41.519
marked even more so. And so it was

00:13:38.560 --> 00:13:43.199
like you were

00:13:41.519 --> 00:13:46.720
being watched. It was a surveillance

00:13:43.200 --> 00:13:48.720
state. It was really weird. It was

00:13:46.720 --> 00:13:51.200
like a library, is

00:13:48.720 --> 00:13:56.440
what I want to call it. Within a couple

00:13:51.200 --> 00:14:01.440
of months, I would say I saw

00:13:56.440 --> 00:14:03.760
a football field with piles of Bibles,

00:14:01.440 --> 00:14:06.160
probably three or four stories

00:14:03.760 --> 00:14:09.199
high. It was massive—just massive.

00:14:06.160 --> 00:14:12.880
They were all being burned. All the

00:14:09.199 --> 00:14:15.359
Bibles were burned by his order.

00:14:12.880 --> 00:14:16.959
Like I said,

00:14:15.360 --> 00:14:18.240
the gasoline was all over

00:14:16.959 --> 00:14:20.160
them. They were thrown into the fire, and

00:14:18.240 --> 00:14:22.320
it was incredible. Just

00:14:20.160 --> 00:14:24.920
massive amounts of smoke and the Bibles

00:14:22.320 --> 00:14:32.240
all burning.

00:14:24.920 --> 00:14:34.639
Then I saw these flags

00:14:32.240 --> 00:14:36.959
that he put on every single courthouse.

00:14:34.639 --> 00:14:38.720
If you had a country flag, like the

00:14:36.959 --> 00:14:41.359
United States of America or Europe,

00:14:38.720 --> 00:14:44.880
those flags were taken down

00:14:41.360 --> 00:14:48.800
and his flag was put up. It

00:14:44.880 --> 00:14:51.760
was black,

00:14:51.760 --> 00:15:00.480
green, and white, and it had these

00:14:56.600 --> 00:15:03.720
gold swords that were all in the

00:15:00.480 --> 00:15:07.199
center of it—massive

00:15:03.720 --> 00:15:08.920
swords, like a

00:15:11.519 --> 00:15:15.360
saber, is what I want to call it. It was

00:15:13.519 --> 00:15:19.279
a massive sword in

00:15:15.360 --> 00:15:21.040
the center of this thing, and each color

00:15:19.279 --> 00:15:25.600
represented

00:15:21.040 --> 00:15:27.079
a terrorist group, ISIS

00:15:28.920 --> 00:15:34.399
and others. I'm not going to even

00:15:32.160 --> 00:15:36.399
go there because I don't know

00:15:34.399 --> 00:15:38.000
all their names, but

00:15:39.839 --> 00:15:44.880
each was

00:15:42.720 --> 00:15:47.600
a terrorist group,

00:15:44.880 --> 00:15:52.160
and they're all being thanked for

00:15:47.600 --> 00:15:55.040
bringing in his reign

00:15:52.160 --> 00:15:59.719
because they supported this so much.

00:15:59.720 --> 00:16:07.720
After that,

00:16:07.720 --> 00:16:15.680
he puts his flag on the

00:16:11.759 --> 00:16:18.399
buildings, and then this is

00:16:15.680 --> 00:16:21.199
what happens next. I go with

00:16:18.399 --> 00:16:26.800
Jesus to this other area. In this, I

00:16:21.199 --> 00:16:29.758
see people on Fridays. Every Friday,

00:16:26.800 --> 00:16:33.120
you're required to worship him. Every

00:16:29.759 --> 00:16:36.240
Friday, they all had white outfits on.

00:16:33.120 --> 00:16:39.680
Every person in the world was required

00:16:36.240 --> 00:16:42.399
to wear a white outfit, and they had

00:16:39.680 --> 00:16:45.120
white garments on their heads. The women

00:16:42.399 --> 00:16:47.839
did. And men had white garments on their

00:16:45.120 --> 00:16:51.680
heads. They had white robes on and

00:16:47.839 --> 00:16:55.440
they were all in single file lines.

00:16:51.680 --> 00:16:58.479
Every line was

00:16:55.440 --> 00:17:00.240
perfect and they were all side by side.

00:16:58.480 --> 00:17:03.640
You were required to get on

00:17:00.240 --> 00:17:08.480
your knees and worship.

00:17:03.640 --> 00:17:12.160
I saw these massive screens—huge screens

00:17:08.480 --> 00:17:14.559
all on the side of the

00:17:12.160 --> 00:17:16.959
buildings of these courthouses. On

00:17:14.559 --> 00:17:20.520
Fridays, he would appear wherever you

00:17:16.959 --> 00:17:23.280
were. If it was America or Europe or

00:17:20.520 --> 00:17:25.520
whatever, you would go to this place of

00:17:23.280 --> 00:17:27.599
worship on Fridays and look at

00:17:25.520 --> 00:17:31.200
the screen. They would

00:17:27.599 --> 00:17:32.480
worship him at those screens and it was

00:17:31.200 --> 00:17:33.840
all over the place, but they were always

00:17:32.480 --> 00:17:36.400
in white robes. They were always in these

00:17:33.840 --> 00:17:39.520
single lines and it was in

00:17:36.400 --> 00:17:43.039
town square areas. What's

00:17:39.520 --> 00:17:45.600
really interesting is that I

00:17:43.039 --> 00:17:47.840
watch a lot of videos on YouTube of

00:17:45.600 --> 00:17:50.639
people walking tours and stuff.

00:17:47.840 --> 00:17:53.840
There's a place in Rome that I saw that

00:17:50.640 --> 00:17:57.440
it happens at. There are places

00:17:53.840 --> 00:17:59.280
in my town where I live now.

00:17:57.440 --> 00:18:01.760
There's a place here and there's a place in

00:17:59.280 --> 00:18:05.678
another town not too far from me

00:18:01.760 --> 00:18:09.039
where

00:18:05.679 --> 00:18:10.679
it's being required to worship.

00:18:10.679 --> 00:18:19.760
Very interesting stuff. So Christians left.

00:18:14.559 --> 00:18:25.280
Then it goes off of him and I

00:18:19.760 --> 00:18:27.280
see Christians that were left. Now,

00:18:25.280 --> 00:18:29.240
this is the part that gets hard, and

00:18:27.280 --> 00:18:33.360
there's probably a lot of

00:18:29.240 --> 00:18:36.640
you that will disagree with this or

00:18:33.360 --> 00:18:39.280
get angry about it, but I have to

00:18:36.640 --> 00:18:42.360
tell you what I saw. It is

00:18:39.280 --> 00:18:46.600
what it is.

00:18:42.360 --> 00:18:49.439
A lot of the grace message that was

00:18:46.600 --> 00:18:51.199
preached, people lived a compromising

00:18:49.440 --> 00:18:54.440
lifestyle.

00:18:51.200 --> 00:18:59.440
They were living like the

00:18:54.440 --> 00:19:01.440
world and they got left.

00:18:59.440 --> 00:19:04.640
There were literally thousands

00:19:01.440 --> 00:19:06.240
of Christians here that

00:19:04.640 --> 00:19:07.679
thought they were born again, thought

00:19:06.240 --> 00:19:10.799
that they were living right, and thought

00:19:07.679 --> 00:19:13.520
that they did everything right, but they

00:19:10.799 --> 00:19:16.480
didn't. They were living like the world

00:19:13.520 --> 00:19:18.240
and had an appearance of godliness.

00:19:16.480 --> 00:19:20.000
Their hearts were so far from the Lord,

00:19:18.240 --> 00:19:21.840
but they thought they were with him.

00:19:20.000 --> 00:19:24.080
They were the ones that even like

00:19:21.840 --> 00:19:28.000
the Bible talks about: 'You prophesied in my

00:19:24.080 --> 00:19:29.840
name, you cast out devils in

00:19:28.000 --> 00:19:31.600
my name, you healed the sick in my name.

00:19:29.840 --> 00:19:33.080
Depart from me; I never knew

00:19:31.600 --> 00:19:35.918
you.'That's

00:19:33.080 --> 00:19:37.678
what happened. There were Christians

00:19:35.919 --> 00:19:40.080
everywhere. There

00:19:40.080 --> 00:19:47.760
were pastors that I saw who

00:19:43.840 --> 00:19:51.199
preached that watered-down

00:19:47.760 --> 00:19:54.320
grace message who were left here

00:19:51.200 --> 00:19:56.840
in punishment because

00:19:54.320 --> 00:20:00.559
they were preaching a lukewarm

00:19:56.840 --> 00:20:05.678
gospel. They were left here, and

00:20:00.559 --> 00:20:09.440
those people were as mad as could be.

00:20:05.679 --> 00:20:13.200
It was terrible. They

00:20:09.440 --> 00:20:15.280
were after those preachers that preached

00:20:13.200 --> 00:20:18.559
that way. They said, "You lied to

00:20:15.280 --> 00:20:20.160
us. You didn't tell us the truth."I

00:20:18.559 --> 00:20:22.879
was standing with Jesus the whole time.

00:20:20.160 --> 00:20:26.160
He said to me, "Look at this. Watch

00:20:22.880 --> 00:20:28.080
this. Remember this."He didn't say

00:20:26.160 --> 00:20:32.159
it, but I heard his thoughts. He said,

00:20:28.080 --> 00:20:35.760
"Watch this. Look at this."I

00:20:32.159 --> 00:20:38.480
was gazing upon this area.

00:20:35.760 --> 00:20:41.280
I knew after all this

00:20:38.480 --> 00:20:43.280
happened I was back in time, back

00:20:41.280 --> 00:20:44.960
before the Antichrist was taking over.

00:20:43.280 --> 00:20:47.918
This is at the beginning,

00:20:44.960 --> 00:20:52.400
right after the rapture happens.

00:20:47.919 --> 00:20:56.159
The people are mad. They are very

00:20:52.400 --> 00:20:58.720
angry that they're here. The

00:20:56.159 --> 00:21:00.320
pastors and these leaders—I saw some of

00:20:58.720 --> 00:21:02.799
them, and I'll never mention their names

00:21:00.320 --> 00:21:05.360
because the Lord told me not to. I saw

00:21:02.799 --> 00:21:07.760
people that were on TV

00:21:05.360 --> 00:21:10.559
teaching the gospel on TBN and stuff

00:21:07.760 --> 00:21:14.320
like that—those Christian channels that

00:21:10.559 --> 00:21:16.480
were actually left. Some of them were—like

00:21:14.320 --> 00:21:18.639
two or three. I'm not ever going to

00:21:16.480 --> 00:21:20.400
say who they were, but I'm going to tell

00:21:18.640 --> 00:21:24.480
you that they were here. There were some

00:21:20.400 --> 00:21:28.559
folks here, and they were

00:21:24.480 --> 00:21:31.520
very angry

00:21:28.559 --> 00:21:34.918
and ready to kill them.

00:21:31.520 --> 00:21:37.080
It was awful. I

00:21:34.919 --> 00:21:41.679
saw one angry Christian

00:21:37.080 --> 00:21:44.240
lady that I know very well.

00:21:41.679 --> 00:21:46.880
I worked at a church for 13

00:21:44.240 --> 00:21:48.320
years; I was a janitor there. She

00:21:46.880 --> 00:21:51.360
was one of the members there at the

00:21:48.320 --> 00:21:54.320
church where I was. I was looking up,

00:21:51.360 --> 00:21:56.719
and she looked up at the heavens and

00:21:54.320 --> 00:21:59.879
she flipped the Lord off. She gave the

00:21:56.720 --> 00:22:04.360
Lord the middle finger and she said some expletives, and

00:21:59.880 --> 00:22:07.200
it was very

00:22:04.360 --> 00:22:10.000
bad. I was watching them all just

00:22:07.200 --> 00:22:12.559
turn on God. They were angry,

00:22:10.000 --> 00:22:15.559
turning on people. There were

00:22:12.559 --> 00:22:18.879
groups of them that were building

00:22:15.559 --> 00:22:20.960
colonies. They started saying, "We've got to

00:22:18.880 --> 00:22:23.840
get prepared. It's fixing to get really

00:22:20.960 --> 00:22:26.120
bad. We've got to get our stuff around.

00:22:23.840 --> 00:22:29.439
We know what's happened. We know what's coming."A

00:22:26.120 --> 00:22:31.439
lot of them did. "We've got

00:22:29.440 --> 00:22:34.000
to go to the mountains. We've got to go

00:22:31.440 --> 00:22:35.600
to places of refuge. We've got to go now

00:22:34.000 --> 00:22:37.480
because we're running out of time. This

00:22:35.600 --> 00:22:42.158
is fixing to get bad really fast."I

00:22:37.480 --> 00:22:45.039
saw these people

00:22:42.159 --> 00:22:48.080
try to have a camaraderie. There were

00:22:45.039 --> 00:22:50.039
families that were left. And this is

00:22:48.080 --> 00:22:56.399
another thing:

00:22:50.039 --> 00:22:59.440
everybody below the age of 15 was gone.

00:22:56.400 --> 00:23:02.640
All the little children were gone. All

00:22:59.440 --> 00:23:05.440
of the younger teenagers and

00:23:02.640 --> 00:23:08.320
pre-teens were gone. They all

00:23:05.440 --> 00:23:10.960
got sucked up in the rapture. But

00:23:08.320 --> 00:23:13.678
anybody that was age of accountability and

00:23:10.960 --> 00:23:15.919
older was left if you didn't know Jesus

00:23:13.679 --> 00:23:19.679
Christ and have a relationship with him.

00:23:15.919 --> 00:23:21.000
I watched these younger people

00:23:19.679 --> 00:23:24.320
go with their

00:23:21.000 --> 00:23:27.840
families. During the

00:23:24.320 --> 00:23:30.399
tribulation, I saw children

00:23:27.840 --> 00:23:34.158
being born. This part is

00:23:30.400 --> 00:23:34.159
really hard.

00:23:34.600 --> 00:23:41.918
I watched how

00:23:39.039 --> 00:23:44.480
the Christians all got together.

00:23:44.480 --> 00:23:49.400
They all go to

00:23:47.200 --> 00:23:53.600
these mountain

00:23:49.400 --> 00:23:58.240
areas and dig massive holes in the side of

00:23:53.600 --> 00:24:00.959
the mountains. They were

00:23:58.240 --> 00:24:02.799
trying to keep warm because

00:24:00.960 --> 00:24:05.679
you couldn't stay in your

00:24:02.799 --> 00:24:07.918
house. You couldn't go into

00:24:05.679 --> 00:24:09.600
town and buy groceries because the

00:24:07.919 --> 00:24:12.960
mark of the beast is coming. I'm going

00:24:09.600 --> 00:24:15.600
to tell you about it; I saw how

00:24:12.960 --> 00:24:18.640
it happens, how the mark of the

00:24:15.600 --> 00:24:20.879
beast changes you, and how they put it

00:24:18.640 --> 00:24:23.679
in your forehead.

00:24:20.880 --> 00:24:26.080
I'll get to that—I don't want

00:24:23.679 --> 00:24:28.720
to skip around too much or

00:24:26.080 --> 00:24:30.559
make this too long as

00:24:28.720 --> 00:24:34.760
I respect people's time.

00:24:34.760 --> 00:24:41.919
The Christians try to move

00:24:37.679 --> 00:24:44.720
at night. I was staying with

00:24:41.919 --> 00:24:47.679
Jesus, and he took me to a

00:24:44.720 --> 00:24:50.159
field. All I knew was it was

00:24:47.679 --> 00:24:51.919
dark outside, and the

00:24:50.159 --> 00:24:53.520
Christians were moving from place to

00:24:51.919 --> 00:24:55.919
place at night because they couldn't move during

00:24:53.520 --> 00:24:58.200
the day without being spotted. They were

00:24:55.919 --> 00:25:00.840
trying to get to places of

00:24:58.200 --> 00:25:04.000
safety.

00:25:00.840 --> 00:25:07.918
The farmers

00:25:04.000 --> 00:25:09.760
had guns like.22s and

00:25:07.919 --> 00:25:11.520
rifles, so there were still

00:25:09.760 --> 00:25:14.720
firearms and

00:25:11.520 --> 00:25:18.000
ways of protection for farmers, but

00:25:14.720 --> 00:25:20.720
I didn't see many other people with guns.

00:25:18.000 --> 00:25:23.440
The Christians didn't have guns. I

00:25:20.720 --> 00:25:25.440
don't know why—nothing

00:25:23.440 --> 00:25:27.360
was really said about that—but I know

00:25:25.440 --> 00:25:30.480
the farmers did. I remember

00:25:27.360 --> 00:25:32.879
seeing one place where these

00:25:30.480 --> 00:25:36.320
Christians were trying to go through a

00:25:32.880 --> 00:25:39.039
pasture, and dogs

00:25:36.320 --> 00:25:40.720
barking alerted the

00:25:39.039 --> 00:25:43.520
farmer inside the house. He flipped

00:25:40.720 --> 00:25:45.919
the light on, and he had a.22 in his

00:25:43.520 --> 00:25:49.200
hand. I know it was a.22. He fired

00:25:45.919 --> 00:25:52.000
it and called the authorities to

00:25:49.200 --> 00:25:54.000
tell them

00:25:54.000 --> 00:25:57.360
people were moving at night. He didn't

00:25:56.000 --> 00:25:58.480
know if they were Christians,

00:25:57.360 --> 00:26:00.000
but I knew they were.

00:26:01.640 --> 00:26:09.159
Then I saw men in black armored

00:26:05.600 --> 00:26:12.240
Hummer trucks with

00:26:09.159 --> 00:26:14.159
blue,

00:26:12.240 --> 00:26:16.240
infrared-looking

00:26:14.159 --> 00:26:18.240
lights inside

00:26:16.240 --> 00:26:20.880
the back.

00:26:18.240 --> 00:26:23.200
They were all black with blacked-out

00:26:20.880 --> 00:26:25.279
windows. As they drove,

00:26:23.200 --> 00:26:28.799
the

00:26:25.279 --> 00:26:31.440
Christians tried to put cement

00:26:28.799 --> 00:26:33.760
blocks in the road to slow

00:26:31.440 --> 00:26:36.159
them down so they would have enough time

00:26:33.760 --> 00:26:38.158
to run away as fast as they could. They would try to throw things in the road to slow their approach, and they were running as

00:26:36.159 --> 00:26:39.760
fast as they could to try to get away.

00:26:49.360 --> 00:26:55.439
These men

00:26:52.080 --> 00:26:57.678
had black face masks on, like

00:26:55.440 --> 00:26:59.919
COVID masks, and

00:26:57.679 --> 00:27:02.400
black

00:26:59.919 --> 00:27:04.320
hoods, and they would jump out. They

00:27:02.400 --> 00:27:06.640
had black outfits on with these vests and

00:27:04.320 --> 00:27:10.480
would jump out of these

00:27:06.640 --> 00:27:12.159
black cars with these guns. But

00:27:10.480 --> 00:27:14.000
this is what's weird: I've never seen

00:27:12.159 --> 00:27:15.840
one of these before. I've tried to

00:27:14.000 --> 00:27:17.760
find them online and I can't;

00:27:15.840 --> 00:27:21.360
I've never seen this before. It was

00:27:17.760 --> 00:27:23.760
a pulse. They took these black guns and

00:27:21.360 --> 00:27:25.840
pointed them and

00:27:23.760 --> 00:27:28.240
shot, but it wasn't a

00:27:25.840 --> 00:27:31.199
bullet. It was electric,

00:27:28.240 --> 00:27:33.360
like an electromagnetic pulse,

00:27:31.200 --> 00:27:36.159
and it just stuns you, but it didn't

00:27:33.360 --> 00:27:38.320
have any stun to it like the

00:27:36.159 --> 00:27:40.559
cords that come out like they have now.

00:27:38.320 --> 00:27:43.279
It was some kind of

00:27:40.559 --> 00:27:45.120
wave of energy that came

00:27:43.279 --> 00:27:47.840
out of these things and knocked you

00:27:45.120 --> 00:27:50.799
senseless for a couple of seconds. They

00:27:47.840 --> 00:27:53.279
didn't have to reload it; they just

00:27:50.799 --> 00:27:55.120
pointed it, and

00:27:53.279 --> 00:27:57.039
the people running fell out on the ground.

00:27:57.039 --> 00:28:01.279
They would pass out right there, and by the time

00:27:59.600 --> 00:28:04.080
they would get up, it was too

00:28:01.279 --> 00:28:07.799
late; they were held captive.

00:28:04.080 --> 00:28:11.639
These men would give them an

00:28:07.799 --> 00:28:15.760
ultimatum. I saw a

00:28:11.640 --> 00:28:18.000
woman and she had these two young children—a

00:28:15.760 --> 00:28:19.840
boy and a girl

00:28:18.000 --> 00:28:22.320
born during the Tribulation. They

00:28:19.840 --> 00:28:24.600
were probably three or four

00:28:22.320 --> 00:28:29.200
years old, maybe more. They were

00:28:24.600 --> 00:28:32.480
talking, so they were young,

00:28:29.200 --> 00:28:34.919
maybe five.

00:28:32.480 --> 00:28:37.799
They said, 'We're going to give the

00:28:34.919 --> 00:28:41.919
children the chip

00:28:37.799 --> 00:28:44.158
first, and if you don't deny your Jesus,

00:28:41.919 --> 00:28:46.960
we're going to cut your kids'heads off.

00:28:44.159 --> 00:28:49.440
We're going to cut their heads off.'Or

00:28:46.960 --> 00:28:51.360
you

00:28:49.440 --> 00:28:55.880
could take the chip. They gave

00:28:51.360 --> 00:29:00.039
them an ultimatum. The dad said,

00:28:55.880 --> 00:29:03.120
'No, we're not taking the mark. We will

00:29:00.039 --> 00:29:06.240
die.'The

00:29:06.240 --> 00:29:12.799
dad said, 'We're most certainly

00:29:10.880 --> 00:29:15.440
not taking the mark.'The mother

00:29:12.799 --> 00:29:17.840
said, 'No, you can't cut my babies'heads off!'because

00:29:15.440 --> 00:29:20.640
the man had this huge

00:29:17.840 --> 00:29:22.480
sickle, a huge sword, in his hand. He was getting ready—he had the baby's head like this—and

00:29:20.640 --> 00:29:25.600
he was getting ready

00:29:25.600 --> 00:29:30.799
to just go and slice

00:29:28.399 --> 00:29:34.719
that kid's head off right there. There

00:29:30.799 --> 00:29:38.799
was no mercy. There was no conscience

00:29:34.720 --> 00:29:41.279
about it. It was just the way it was.

00:29:38.799 --> 00:29:46.399
And the dad cried out and said, "No, you

00:29:41.279 --> 00:29:50.240
must not take the mark."And when he

00:29:46.399 --> 00:29:53.360
said that, they cut his

00:29:50.240 --> 00:29:56.880
head off right there. And I'm talking it

00:29:53.360 --> 00:29:59.918
fell and rolled at my feet, and I could

00:29:56.880 --> 00:30:03.440
smell his blood. That's how

00:29:59.919 --> 00:30:05.679
awful it was. Jesus stood there with me

00:30:03.440 --> 00:30:07.840
the whole time, and he never made a

00:30:05.679 --> 00:30:11.679
comment about it. He just told me to

00:30:07.840 --> 00:30:14.480
look. And so I looked and I watched

00:30:11.679 --> 00:30:16.720
the woman, and she said, "I'll take the

00:30:14.480 --> 00:30:19.600
mark. I'll take it. I'll take the

00:30:16.720 --> 00:30:22.559
chip. Don't take

00:30:19.600 --> 00:30:25.120
their heads."And this is what is so

00:30:22.559 --> 00:30:29.399
incredible; it's absolutely amazing

00:30:25.120 --> 00:30:31.360
about this part. They take this chip, and

00:30:29.399 --> 00:30:34.479
instantaneously those children were

00:30:31.360 --> 00:30:37.279
crying because they just saw their dad

00:30:34.480 --> 00:30:40.240
die right in front of them. And the mom

00:30:37.279 --> 00:30:42.480
is crying and she's bawling her eyes out

00:30:40.240 --> 00:30:45.279
because she saw her husband die right in

00:30:42.480 --> 00:30:48.559
front of her. And the moment she takes

00:30:45.279 --> 00:30:50.279
the chip, the baby, the two children, and

00:30:48.559 --> 00:30:52.360
her

00:30:50.279 --> 00:30:55.200
instantaneously lose

00:30:52.360 --> 00:30:57.039
emotion. They don't

00:30:55.200 --> 00:31:00.880
have any emotion on their face.

00:30:57.039 --> 00:31:02.879
They totally lose the crying. It's

00:31:00.880 --> 00:31:05.200
like they went like a zombie right there

00:31:02.880 --> 00:31:07.760
in front of me. Their minds and

00:31:05.200 --> 00:31:11.720
everything had a peace again. It's like

00:31:07.760 --> 00:31:16.080
the chip sent a peace to their brain

00:31:11.720 --> 00:31:18.640
somehow. I don't know how; all I

00:31:16.080 --> 00:31:21.760
know is the chip did something to them

00:31:18.640 --> 00:31:24.080
and it made them calm. It put off

00:31:21.760 --> 00:31:27.520
some kind of endorphin in them, and they

00:31:24.080 --> 00:31:29.439
just went cold in their face, like

00:31:27.520 --> 00:31:31.440
they're not there. It's like, "Hello,

00:31:29.440 --> 00:31:33.600
you're not there,"and they were not

00:31:31.440 --> 00:31:34.919
crying about him anymore. It's

00:31:33.600 --> 00:31:40.879
like they didn't

00:31:34.919 --> 00:31:45.039
care. And so I saw that, and then I

00:31:40.880 --> 00:31:47.760
saw a man trying to commit suicide, and

00:31:45.039 --> 00:31:50.320
he already had the mark. He had the chip

00:31:47.760 --> 00:31:54.000
in his hand, and he was standing on a

00:31:50.320 --> 00:31:57.360
major bridge, and all of a sudden the

00:31:54.000 --> 00:31:59.960
chip sent a signal to his brain and

00:31:57.360 --> 00:32:02.879
calmed him down and he did not kill

00:31:59.960 --> 00:32:05.840
himself. I don't understand why; I don't

00:32:02.880 --> 00:32:08.240
understand how. All I know is that chip

00:32:05.840 --> 00:32:11.279
produced some kind of signal, some

00:32:08.240 --> 00:32:13.240
kind of endorphin somehow, and calmed his

00:32:11.279 --> 00:32:15.760
mind down, and

00:32:13.240 --> 00:32:18.559
instantaneously he became calm and he

00:32:15.760 --> 00:32:21.039
did not jump off that bridge. It

00:32:18.559 --> 00:32:23.279
knew; I don't know how it knew that you

00:32:21.039 --> 00:32:25.760
were fixing to do something like that.

00:32:23.279 --> 00:32:28.399
Then I would see people mowing their

00:32:25.760 --> 00:32:30.799
grass and I would walk by them, but they

00:32:28.399 --> 00:32:32.639
couldn't see me. I would walk by

00:32:30.799 --> 00:32:35.279
them and they were mowing, but they were

00:32:32.640 --> 00:32:36.640
not there. It's like you could go, "Hello,"but

00:32:35.279 --> 00:32:39.200
you were just in

00:32:36.640 --> 00:32:41.760
another world, way out there,

00:32:39.200 --> 00:32:43.600
like a zombie. It was weird.

00:32:41.760 --> 00:32:46.158
They were just mowing their grass

00:32:43.600 --> 00:32:48.959
like robots, but the chip would

00:32:46.159 --> 00:32:52.440
bring something to their biological

00:32:48.960 --> 00:32:54.600
brain. I don't get it.

00:32:52.440 --> 00:32:58.480
Another thing I thought was

00:32:54.600 --> 00:33:00.559
interesting is that I

00:32:58.480 --> 00:33:02.919
watched them. Jesus took me to a place

00:33:00.559 --> 00:33:06.399
in a town, and there were these

00:33:02.919 --> 00:33:09.679
barricades all over, massive

00:33:06.399 --> 00:33:13.678
gray barricades, huge.

00:33:09.679 --> 00:33:16.960
There were men with armed guards

00:33:13.679 --> 00:33:19.440
and guns all around.

00:33:16.960 --> 00:33:21.840
You would have to go

00:33:19.440 --> 00:33:25.039
through these barricades to get into

00:33:21.840 --> 00:33:27.519
these towns; you had to have your

00:33:25.039 --> 00:33:30.000
chip in your hand. If you

00:33:27.519 --> 00:33:33.039
didn't have the chip, you couldn't

00:33:30.000 --> 00:33:35.039
get in, and they would

00:33:33.039 --> 00:33:36.799
offer you the chip or you would die.

00:33:35.039 --> 00:33:38.720
They would kill you right there—no

00:33:36.799 --> 00:33:42.240
questions. If you didn't take

00:33:38.720 --> 00:33:45.200
it, they'd cut your head off.

00:33:42.240 --> 00:33:48.080
There was a woman—I

00:33:45.200 --> 00:33:50.559
remember her face. She was a white

00:33:48.080 --> 00:33:53.120
woman with brown hair, and she was

00:33:50.559 --> 00:33:55.200
standing in line.

00:33:53.120 --> 00:33:58.239
A lot of people, though not everyone,

00:33:55.200 --> 00:34:01.360
had a bruise on their

00:33:58.240 --> 00:34:05.000
head; it was a burn sore. The body

00:34:01.360 --> 00:34:08.159
had a reaction to the chip and it caused

00:34:05.000 --> 00:34:10.960
sores on people's heads. It was like

00:34:08.159 --> 00:34:13.520
burn sores, and there were burn sores on

00:34:10.960 --> 00:34:15.800
their hands—not everyone, though.

00:34:13.520 --> 00:34:19.040
She was trying to mimic it with

00:34:15.800 --> 00:34:22.720
makeup, trying to put makeup on her

00:34:19.040 --> 00:34:24.040
hand to make it look like she had a burn

00:34:22.719 --> 00:34:27.199
sore.

00:34:24.040 --> 00:34:29.079
She was standing in line, and

00:34:27.199 --> 00:34:32.319
when she got up to go in through the

00:34:29.079 --> 00:34:35.119
gate, they saw that she was trying to

00:34:32.320 --> 00:34:38.000
fake it. People were so desperate

00:34:35.119 --> 00:34:40.560
for food and for whatever resources they

00:34:38.000 --> 00:34:43.040
could get into the towns that

00:34:40.560 --> 00:34:45.918
they were willing to do

00:34:43.040 --> 00:34:48.159
whatever it took. She was a Christian,

00:34:45.918 --> 00:34:50.399
basically. I guess I don't know who

00:34:48.159 --> 00:34:53.599
she really was;

00:34:50.399 --> 00:34:56.319
the moment they saw

00:34:53.599 --> 00:35:00.119
her faking it, they cut her head off

00:34:56.320 --> 00:35:02.480
right there. There was no time for even

00:35:00.119 --> 00:35:04.880
repentance. They just

00:35:02.480 --> 00:35:06.880
took a sickle-sword and

00:35:04.880 --> 00:35:08.880
cut her head off like it was

00:35:06.880 --> 00:35:11.520
nothing. Her head rolled out,

00:35:08.880 --> 00:35:14.400
and people in line who were

00:35:11.520 --> 00:35:16.480
watching acted like it was nothing. There

00:35:14.400 --> 00:35:18.560
was no emotion. I'm telling you,

00:35:16.480 --> 00:35:21.760
there was no emotion to these people;

00:35:18.560 --> 00:35:23.920
they were gone. It was weird.

00:35:23.920 --> 00:35:26.960
I'm just telling you what I saw and I'm

00:35:25.520 --> 00:35:28.640
trying to figure it out myself. I'm still trying

00:35:26.960 --> 00:35:31.359
to figure out the nanotechnology. And the only thing

00:35:28.640 --> 00:35:34.960
that I think is really close to this nanotechnology is what

00:35:31.359 --> 00:35:37.839
a very

00:35:34.960 --> 00:35:39.520
rich man here in America is working on—I

00:35:37.839 --> 00:35:42.160
don't want to say his name. If you go

00:35:39.520 --> 00:35:44.320
and look at it, he's working on

00:35:42.160 --> 00:35:47.520
chips right now on pigs. That's all I

00:35:44.320 --> 00:35:51.599
can say. And it's very similar. But

00:35:47.520 --> 00:35:54.079
this chip goes—it's very small,

00:35:51.599 --> 00:35:58.560
like a

00:35:54.079 --> 00:36:01.440
very small square.

00:35:58.560 --> 00:36:03.440
I don't know how it gets power, if it

00:36:01.440 --> 00:36:05.440
gets it from your body's energy. I don't

00:36:03.440 --> 00:36:07.520
know, because it didn't have a battery.

00:36:05.440 --> 00:36:11.040
There's no way a battery could be that

00:36:07.520 --> 00:36:12.880
small.

00:36:11.040 --> 00:36:14.800
Like I said, these men carried around

00:36:12.880 --> 00:36:16.880
these guns that were like waves of

00:36:14.800 --> 00:36:20.560
energy and they knocked you down. It's

00:36:16.880 --> 00:36:23.359
like super sci-fi, but it's not.

00:36:20.560 --> 00:36:24.839
It's legit what I saw.

00:36:24.839 --> 00:36:32.078
Then I saw

00:36:28.560 --> 00:36:33.440
the Christians again, and this

00:36:32.079 --> 00:36:34.800
is part of it.

00:36:33.440 --> 00:36:36.320
I'm praying I'm not skipping around too

00:36:34.800 --> 00:36:39.760
much, because I'm

00:36:36.320 --> 00:36:41.480
telling you how I remember it.

00:36:39.760 --> 00:36:45.520
They were digging these

00:36:41.480 --> 00:36:47.440
foxholes. And the winters were terrible.

00:36:45.520 --> 00:36:50.320
The further north they went in the

00:36:47.440 --> 00:36:52.400
mountains, the colder the temperatures

00:36:50.320 --> 00:36:55.040
were. I don't know what kind of

00:36:52.400 --> 00:36:57.920
catastrophic events of nature happened there,

00:36:55.040 --> 00:37:02.079
because I didn't see that. All I know

00:36:57.920 --> 00:37:05.960
is that the winters were awful, and

00:37:02.079 --> 00:37:09.920
people died from starvation and the

00:37:05.960 --> 00:37:13.200
cold quickly. It was bad.

00:37:09.920 --> 00:37:16.040
Here comes another part:

00:37:13.200 --> 00:37:20.000
I look up in the

00:37:16.040 --> 00:37:23.560
sky because I hear these noises,

00:37:20.000 --> 00:37:26.800
and there are thousands of drones.

00:37:23.560 --> 00:37:30.078
Thousands. No joke. Thousands. They

00:37:26.800 --> 00:37:33.200
are all in sequence with each other,

00:37:30.079 --> 00:37:36.119
flying across the sky,

00:37:33.200 --> 00:37:39.919
scanning the horizon and scanning

00:37:36.119 --> 00:37:42.720
everybody. The chip in

00:37:39.920 --> 00:37:44.880
your hand or your forehead would report

00:37:42.720 --> 00:37:48.399
back to these

00:37:44.880 --> 00:37:50.160
drones that you had it. These

00:37:48.400 --> 00:37:52.800
drones would fly throughout the

00:37:50.160 --> 00:37:54.720
woods, throughout all areas, the

00:37:52.800 --> 00:37:56.320
oceans, everywhere. They were flying

00:37:54.720 --> 00:37:57.520
throughout all of America,

00:37:56.320 --> 00:37:59.440
all over the place. You could

00:37:57.520 --> 00:38:02.480
literally

00:37:59.440 --> 00:38:05.359
hear them coming, and they could sense

00:38:02.480 --> 00:38:09.760
your body heat,

00:38:05.359 --> 00:38:12.400
your motion, and everything. So, you

00:38:09.760 --> 00:38:14.560
couldn't hide from them. The only way I

00:38:12.400 --> 00:38:17.640
saw that the Christians could hide from

00:38:14.560 --> 00:38:20.960
them was digging into the side of the

00:38:17.640 --> 00:38:23.839
hills. The drones were looking for

00:38:20.960 --> 00:38:26.000
smoke or gunshots. So the Christians

00:38:23.839 --> 00:38:28.560
couldn't shoot for food—rabbits

00:38:26.000 --> 00:38:31.200
or deer or

00:38:28.560 --> 00:38:34.640
anything that made noise—because the

00:38:31.200 --> 00:38:37.680
drones in the sky could hear

00:38:34.640 --> 00:38:40.720
the noises. They were alerted and

00:38:37.680 --> 00:38:43.839
would swarm to

00:38:40.720 --> 00:38:45.759
that area and see who did it. If you

00:38:43.839 --> 00:38:47.520
had the chip, it would report back and they would

00:38:45.760 --> 00:38:50.079
just go on

00:38:47.520 --> 00:38:52.160
about their business. But if you didn't

00:38:50.079 --> 00:38:53.920
have the chip, they would call for the

00:38:52.160 --> 00:38:55.680
authorities, who would come and

00:38:53.920 --> 00:38:58.000
stay there until they arrived.

00:38:55.680 --> 00:38:59.919
You would run, but

00:38:58.000 --> 00:39:01.200
you couldn't get away. You couldn't get

00:38:59.920 --> 00:39:04.240
away from them because they were up like

00:39:01.200 --> 00:39:06.480
a helicopter. They were flying over, and

00:39:04.240 --> 00:39:08.799
once they found you, you were done.

00:39:06.480 --> 00:39:11.200
They would come and either

00:39:08.800 --> 00:39:14.480
you took the chip or you took the

00:39:11.200 --> 00:39:16.480
mark, or they cut your head off.

00:39:14.480 --> 00:39:18.560
These

00:39:16.480 --> 00:39:21.040
Christians were all on the side of mountains—people

00:39:18.560 --> 00:39:23.200
that were still

00:39:21.040 --> 00:39:26.079
fighting to live and survive, who were

00:39:23.200 --> 00:39:27.759
not living for Jesus

00:39:26.079 --> 00:39:30.920
when they were on the

00:39:27.760 --> 00:39:33.079
earth, but they knew the truth. They

00:39:30.920 --> 00:39:35.680
knew.

00:39:33.079 --> 00:39:38.800
The children were the hardest part

00:39:35.680 --> 00:39:40.799
for me, those born during the

00:39:38.800 --> 00:39:42.400
Tribulation. I know there's a Bible

00:39:40.800 --> 00:39:45.839
verse that says, 'Woe to those that give

00:39:42.400 --> 00:39:48.440
suck in those days.'I believe that

00:39:45.839 --> 00:39:51.160
verse is talking about the

00:39:48.440 --> 00:39:54.480
Tribulation, but

00:39:51.160 --> 00:39:56.879
all I know is that the kids were

00:39:54.480 --> 00:39:58.640
taking it really hard.

00:39:56.880 --> 00:40:00.560
They were going inside, and the

00:39:58.640 --> 00:40:02.240
smoke was coming out of these

00:40:00.560 --> 00:40:05.040
caves. They were trying to keep the

00:40:02.240 --> 00:40:07.520
fires

00:40:05.040 --> 00:40:10.560
really low so that the drones

00:40:07.520 --> 00:40:12.720
couldn't see it. The drones

00:40:10.560 --> 00:40:16.240
would fly throughout the earth, and they

00:40:12.720 --> 00:40:18.480
sounded like swarms of bees beyond

00:40:16.240 --> 00:40:20.319
anything. It was incredibly

00:40:18.480 --> 00:40:21.520
loud. Swarms of bees were

00:40:20.320 --> 00:40:23.040
everywhere, and you knew when they were

00:40:21.520 --> 00:40:25.520
coming because you could hear them from a

00:40:23.040 --> 00:40:28.079
distance. Everybody would scramble,

00:40:25.520 --> 00:40:29.560
trying to get into their safe zone as

00:40:28.079 --> 00:40:33.359
fast as they could to try to hide themselves.

00:40:29.560 --> 00:40:36.799
They

00:40:33.359 --> 00:40:40.000
were made to worship on Fridays. I

00:40:36.800 --> 00:40:40.000
told you about

00:40:40.920 --> 00:40:46.400
the people and

00:40:44.800 --> 00:40:48.440
the mark of the beast; they had the Abomination of Desolation

00:40:46.400 --> 00:40:51.280
chip in their hands.

00:40:51.280 --> 00:40:58.359
Now I want to tell you about the

00:40:54.480 --> 00:41:01.880
Abomination of Desolation.

00:40:58.359 --> 00:41:04.119
I was all of a sudden translated to

00:41:01.880 --> 00:41:08.640
Israel, and

00:41:04.119 --> 00:41:12.240
I see this great big temple. It's on a

00:41:08.640 --> 00:41:14.839
hill, elevated,

00:41:12.240 --> 00:41:19.520
with

00:41:14.839 --> 00:41:23.279
these massive stone columns all

00:41:19.520 --> 00:41:26.000
inside of it and a

00:41:23.280 --> 00:41:28.480
roof. There is

00:41:26.000 --> 00:41:31.119
a place

00:41:28.480 --> 00:41:34.480
where

00:41:31.119 --> 00:41:37.400
people can come at the base of

00:41:34.480 --> 00:41:40.560
this temple.

00:41:37.400 --> 00:41:43.119
I'm standing

00:41:40.560 --> 00:41:45.920
at the base of

00:41:43.119 --> 00:41:49.760
the temple with Jesus,

00:41:45.920 --> 00:41:51.760
looking up. The

00:41:49.760 --> 00:41:55.280
temple is

00:41:51.760 --> 00:41:57.680
elevated,

00:41:55.280 --> 00:42:01.520
and the Antichrist has a

00:41:57.680 --> 00:42:06.319
podium. He's standing in between

00:42:01.520 --> 00:42:09.920
those big columns with a man on either side of him.

00:42:06.319 --> 00:42:12.240
I don't know who

00:42:09.920 --> 00:42:14.800
this man is right here on his other

00:42:12.240 --> 00:42:17.040
hand. I believe he's another form of a

00:42:14.800 --> 00:42:20.760
religion. I'm not familiar with a lot of

00:42:17.040 --> 00:42:23.400
other leaders and other religious

00:42:20.760 --> 00:42:29.640
beliefs.

00:42:23.400 --> 00:42:34.480
I'll say that he had olive skin, lightning bolts,

00:42:29.640 --> 00:42:38.078
and darker hair also. But that's

00:42:34.480 --> 00:42:38.079
all I'm going to say about that.

00:42:38.440 --> 00:42:46.160
So, I'm looking up and there are

00:42:42.079 --> 00:42:50.800
lightning bolts shooting all over the

00:42:46.160 --> 00:42:54.640
sky. I'm talking—it's like

00:42:50.800 --> 00:42:56.480
total chaos, lightning—but none of

00:42:54.640 --> 00:42:59.319
it's touching the ground. It's just

00:42:56.480 --> 00:43:03.599
going all over the sky.

00:42:59.319 --> 00:43:07.400
And the Lord won't let me see his eyes

00:43:03.599 --> 00:43:10.640
from here, around all this.

00:43:07.400 --> 00:43:13.520
But I see the Antichrist again,

00:43:10.640 --> 00:43:16.720
and he's standing there proclaiming that

00:43:13.520 --> 00:43:19.920
he is God on the Temple Mount. And he

00:43:16.720 --> 00:43:22.240
has at this time—not every time

00:43:19.920 --> 00:43:25.040
that I see him, like when he was

00:43:22.240 --> 00:43:28.720
at the beginning when

00:43:25.040 --> 00:43:30.800
he first appears in Berlin—he didn't

00:43:28.720 --> 00:43:32.240
have a beard. I didn't see his eyes

00:43:30.800 --> 00:43:34.240
there, but I saw that he had olive

00:43:32.240 --> 00:43:36.720
skin and he was clean-cut and clean-shaven

00:43:34.240 --> 00:43:40.160
at this time. I don't

00:43:36.720 --> 00:43:43.279
know why. But at this time, he has a

00:43:40.160 --> 00:43:45.118
beard and it's salt and pepper—like

00:43:43.280 --> 00:43:48.880
black and white—a

00:43:45.119 --> 00:43:51.920
beard, and the sides of his

00:43:48.880 --> 00:43:54.880
hair were black and white. They were not

00:43:51.920 --> 00:43:57.520
strictly white or strictly black. He had

00:43:54.880 --> 00:44:00.640
spots of gray coming through his

00:43:57.520 --> 00:44:04.880
hair similar to mine. But he had

00:44:00.640 --> 00:44:09.920
hair; he wasn't bald. He had a

00:44:04.880 --> 00:44:12.760
white turban hat on, like a rag-type

00:44:09.920 --> 00:44:16.400
garment on his head.

00:44:12.760 --> 00:44:18.480
I could see that—like I

00:44:16.400 --> 00:44:22.200
said, I couldn't see his eyes—but he had

00:44:18.480 --> 00:44:25.720
some kind of glasses on.

00:44:22.200 --> 00:44:31.439
He was about 5'11"to

00:44:25.720 --> 00:44:32.959
6 feet tall from what

00:44:31.440 --> 00:44:34.880
I could see while looking up

00:44:32.960 --> 00:44:38.440
like this because it's in

00:44:34.880 --> 00:44:44.960
person now. He was probably

00:44:38.440 --> 00:44:47.839
around 195 to 215 pounds

00:44:44.960 --> 00:44:51.200
in weight. I'll describe

00:44:47.839 --> 00:44:54.400
him like this: he carries himself like a

00:44:51.200 --> 00:44:56.160
James Bond. It may sound dumb, but

00:44:54.400 --> 00:45:00.680
I'm just going to say it like this. He

00:44:56.160 --> 00:45:04.560
carries himself very confidently,

00:45:00.680 --> 00:45:07.839
very poised in the way he

00:45:04.560 --> 00:45:10.000
talked, similar to the way Barack Obama

00:45:07.839 --> 00:45:11.920
used to whenever he delivered his

00:45:10.000 --> 00:45:14.000
speeches to the State of the

00:45:11.920 --> 00:45:17.640
Union. The way he carried

00:45:14.000 --> 00:45:22.560
himself, he spoke very intelligently;

00:45:17.640 --> 00:45:22.560
he

00:45:22.760 --> 00:45:28.200
was very

00:45:25.599 --> 00:45:34.079
poised and

00:45:28.200 --> 00:45:39.118
very precise. He had a way

00:45:34.079 --> 00:45:43.200
to draw you in; he made you like him. It

00:45:39.119 --> 00:45:47.040
was so peaceful, and the way he

00:45:43.200 --> 00:45:47.040
communicated to you

00:45:47.640 --> 00:45:53.440
just brought peace. It

00:45:50.640 --> 00:45:56.160
was really weird, very strange because

00:45:53.440 --> 00:45:58.400
everybody was just fixated on his

00:45:56.160 --> 00:45:59.799
face.

00:45:58.400 --> 00:46:02.640
He brought the

00:45:59.800 --> 00:46:06.000
peace they used to feel, the peace I told

00:46:02.640 --> 00:46:08.160
you about at the beginning that you

00:46:06.000 --> 00:46:10.960
didn't feel anymore. He brought that

00:46:08.160 --> 00:46:14.240
peace you didn't feel. He brought

00:46:10.960 --> 00:46:16.720
that sense of comfort that I said

00:46:14.240 --> 00:46:19.759
every person wakes up with every single

00:46:16.720 --> 00:46:21.839
day and goes to bed with as a

00:46:19.760 --> 00:46:24.000
sinner; they don't even realize it. And

00:46:21.839 --> 00:46:25.839
that's peace. It's like a prayer

00:46:24.000 --> 00:46:28.960
covering that the body of Christ brings

00:46:25.839 --> 00:46:30.880
into this world, and we probably

00:46:28.960 --> 00:46:32.640
don't even realize that

00:46:30.880 --> 00:46:34.800
we bring it. The church doesn't even

00:46:32.640 --> 00:46:36.960
realize the power they have,

00:46:34.800 --> 00:46:39.520
the atmosphere we create

00:46:36.960 --> 00:46:41.160
with our prayers, the atmosphere we

00:46:39.520 --> 00:46:45.920
create

00:46:41.160 --> 00:46:49.759
every day. And then when we're gone,

00:46:45.920 --> 00:46:52.880
it's hell on earth. It's awful. And for

00:46:49.760 --> 00:46:55.040
