is when he speaks, nobody else feels

00:46:55.040 --> 00:47:02.720
that anymore. But he has a falseness, a

00:46:58.280 --> 00:47:05.599
false peace that everybody pursues and

00:47:02.720 --> 00:47:07.598
wants. Again, they're starving for it;

00:47:05.599 --> 00:47:09.520
they don't have it, and so they're

00:47:07.599 --> 00:47:11.680
looking for it. And he has a dirtiness;

00:47:09.520 --> 00:47:13.599
it's a dirty falseness

00:47:11.680 --> 00:47:17.520
that they're all wanting,

00:47:13.599 --> 00:47:18.520
they're all looking for again. And so he

00:47:17.520 --> 00:47:22.119
sucks you

00:47:18.520 --> 00:47:24.680
in.

00:47:22.119 --> 00:47:27.839
At this

00:47:24.680 --> 00:47:29.839
time, during

00:47:27.839 --> 00:47:33.920
this part of the visitation,

00:47:29.839 --> 00:47:36.480
I'm taken out of the earth.

00:47:33.920 --> 00:47:41.680
I'm sucked up out of the earth and

00:47:36.480 --> 00:47:43.520
I go to the edge of heaven and earth,

00:47:41.680 --> 00:47:45.118
and I'm standing there. I can turn

00:47:43.520 --> 00:47:47.800
around and I can look and I see the

00:47:45.119 --> 00:47:51.440
gates of heaven. I see the holy city is

00:47:47.800 --> 00:47:55.319
beautiful all behind me, and Jesus is

00:47:51.440 --> 00:47:56.839
standing right here this time on my

00:47:55.319 --> 00:48:00.319
left.

00:47:56.839 --> 00:48:02.880
And he speaks to me this time and he

00:48:00.319 --> 00:48:04.839
says, 'Look at the earth; I want to show

00:48:02.880 --> 00:48:07.599
you something that's about to take place.'And

00:48:04.839 --> 00:48:09.359
I said,

00:48:07.599 --> 00:48:12.480
'You know, I'm just excited.'I look

00:48:09.359 --> 00:48:14.799
over and I look at the earth and

00:48:12.480 --> 00:48:17.280
it's spinning; I can see it

00:48:14.800 --> 00:48:19.839
moving. And he said, 'Do you

00:48:17.280 --> 00:48:21.359
see each one of those lights down there?'And

00:48:19.839 --> 00:48:23.920
I said, 'Yeah.'He goes, 'Those

00:48:21.359 --> 00:48:26.640
represent souls.'And

00:48:23.920 --> 00:48:30.640
he said there is going to

00:48:26.640 --> 00:48:33.200
be a major revival about to happen

00:48:30.640 --> 00:48:33.200
throughout the earth—a

00:48:33.640 --> 00:48:41.319
final push, a final harvest, a China

00:48:38.960 --> 00:48:44.400
major harvest. It's like—and

00:48:41.319 --> 00:48:46.240
I don't want to add any

00:48:44.400 --> 00:48:48.960
words that he didn't say, but that's

00:48:46.240 --> 00:48:50.799
what he showed me. And

00:48:48.960 --> 00:48:53.040
then he started—I look over at

00:48:50.800 --> 00:48:55.119
him, I'm looking over, and I look at his

00:48:53.040 --> 00:48:58.279
eyes and they're welled up with

00:48:55.119 --> 00:49:01.319
tears. He said, 'Do you see China?'And

00:48:58.280 --> 00:49:05.480
I said, 'Yeah.'He said,

00:49:01.319 --> 00:49:09.960
'They, a lot of them, died for my gospel.'"The

00:49:05.480 --> 00:49:12.800
gospel cost them something, Brandon."He

00:49:09.960 --> 00:49:16.000
looked at him and was so

00:49:12.800 --> 00:49:18.880
filled with joy at the sacrifice

00:49:16.000 --> 00:49:21.359
they gave for the gospel.

00:49:18.880 --> 00:49:24.000
What I saw

00:49:21.359 --> 00:49:27.200
when I was looking over were these gold

00:49:24.000 --> 00:49:29.599
streams. They were like gold

00:49:27.200 --> 00:49:31.439
streets, but they weren't, because I knew

00:49:29.599 --> 00:49:33.920
each one of those lights represented a

00:49:31.440 --> 00:49:36.520
soul. I said, "Lord, what is that?"He

00:49:33.920 --> 00:49:38.920
said, "That's the underground

00:49:36.520 --> 00:49:42.720
churches in China."He

00:49:38.920 --> 00:49:44.960
said, "Each one of those represents

00:49:42.720 --> 00:49:47.520
a soul."It's

00:49:44.960 --> 00:49:49.640
just amazing

00:49:47.520 --> 00:49:52.400
because I'm looking at the Asian

00:49:49.640 --> 00:49:55.598
souls that get saved and

00:49:52.400 --> 00:50:00.079
they spread all throughout Asia. You can

00:49:55.599 --> 00:50:02.880
see these gold veins that go up

00:50:00.079 --> 00:50:07.760
through North Korea, South

00:50:02.880 --> 00:50:10.160
Korea, and Japan.

00:50:07.760 --> 00:50:11.920
Then I looked

00:50:10.160 --> 00:50:13.440
over at the

00:50:11.920 --> 00:50:16.000
Philippines and there were lights in the

00:50:13.440 --> 00:50:18.400
Philippines. Then I looked at Australia

00:50:16.000 --> 00:50:20.280
and there were lights in Australia, and there were

00:50:18.400 --> 00:50:24.240
these circles, like crop

00:50:20.280 --> 00:50:27.520
circles,

00:50:27.520 --> 00:50:35.359
all over

00:50:30.680 --> 00:50:39.040
Europe, including France and Germany. Each country

00:50:35.359 --> 00:50:41.920
had a circle, and some circles were

00:50:39.040 --> 00:50:44.880
bigger than others. Inside each of

00:50:41.920 --> 00:50:47.280
those circles were lights.

00:50:44.880 --> 00:50:49.520
They

00:50:47.280 --> 00:50:51.720
represented

00:50:49.520 --> 00:50:55.359
hotspots for

00:50:51.720 --> 00:50:58.078
revival, major places where people went

00:50:55.359 --> 00:51:00.000
for revival.

00:50:58.079 --> 00:51:01.760
The Lord never said what they represent while I

00:51:00.000 --> 00:51:03.760
was standing there;

00:51:01.760 --> 00:51:06.800
he just told me to look at the souls.

00:51:03.760 --> 00:51:08.800
But

00:51:06.800 --> 00:51:10.880
they were all round circles.

00:51:08.800 --> 00:51:13.520
Then I looked over to the Middle East,

00:51:10.880 --> 00:51:17.359
and there weren't as many there

00:51:13.520 --> 00:51:19.040
as there were in Africa,

00:51:17.359 --> 00:51:21.520
Europe,

00:51:19.040 --> 00:51:24.400
America, Canada, Mexico, and

00:51:21.520 --> 00:51:26.319
South America. In Pakistan, Afghanistan, Iraq, and Iran,

00:51:24.400 --> 00:51:28.800
there was

00:51:28.800 --> 00:51:34.480
revival.

00:51:31.440 --> 00:51:38.240
People were getting

00:51:34.480 --> 00:51:40.559
saved and led to the Lord

00:51:38.240 --> 00:51:42.399
