00:51:48.079 --> 00:51:52.720
some of the other places I saw, though

00:51:50.160 --> 00:51:58.118
it was amazing all over the

00:51:52.720 --> 00:52:02.439
place. America, from coast to

00:51:58.119 --> 00:52:05.040
coast, was lights everywhere—literally

00:52:02.440 --> 00:52:09.400
hundreds of

00:52:05.040 --> 00:52:12.400
thousands, if not millions, of lights

00:52:09.400 --> 00:52:16.920
everywhere. They went all up and

00:52:12.400 --> 00:52:20.480
down the I-35 corridor from Texas to

00:52:16.920 --> 00:52:24.960
Oklahoma. There were major places of

00:52:20.480 --> 00:52:26.880
revival there. Then I saw

00:52:28.520 --> 00:52:32.720
major revival on the West Coast

00:52:31.440 --> 00:52:35.200
and the East Coast. I mean, it was

00:52:32.720 --> 00:52:37.959
everywhere. The revival was everywhere.

00:52:35.200 --> 00:52:41.279
But I know that...

00:52:37.960 --> 00:52:43.599
let me see this. Then,

00:52:41.280 --> 00:52:46.920
what else did I see? I went up

00:52:43.599 --> 00:52:50.480
and I looked behind me,

00:52:46.920 --> 00:52:52.480
and there was a wave coming out of

00:52:50.480 --> 00:52:55.440
