00:52:58.880 --> 00:53:07.119
massive, thick wall.

00:53:02.520 --> 00:53:12.400
And there was a wave.

00:53:07.119 --> 00:53:15.599
This wave was huge, like a tsunami wave—the

00:53:12.400 --> 00:53:17.680
biggest wave you can

00:53:15.599 --> 00:53:20.319
comprehend. It was massive, like a 50-foot

00:53:17.680 --> 00:53:24.078
huge, thick wall of

00:53:20.319 --> 00:53:28.480
