00:53:45.359 --> 00:53:48.960
There were these chariots, and they

00:53:47.040 --> 00:53:51.839
were golden looking fire. It was

00:53:48.960 --> 00:53:54.800
the glory all over these chariots, and

00:53:51.839 --> 00:53:58.160
