00:54:28.559 --> 00:54:34.599
giftings, end-time mantles

00:54:31.400 --> 00:54:37.280
that have

00:54:34.599 --> 00:54:40.480
never been on the earth before, never

00:54:37.280 --> 00:54:43.440
have been seen by anybody on the earth.

00:54:40.480 --> 00:54:46.480
Creative miracles, things that you have

00:54:43.440 --> 00:54:49.200
never experienced on the earth.'Like

00:54:46.480 --> 00:54:52.160
whenever he said, 'And greater works

00:54:49.200 --> 00:54:54.078
will you do.'These are

00:54:52.160 --> 00:54:56.960
