00:55:02.400 --> 00:55:08.640
I can't comprehend in the natural what

00:55:05.040 --> 00:55:14.440
that could be. But I'm just saying these

00:55:08.640 --> 00:55:18.879
were massive

00:55:14.440 --> 00:55:22.760
outpourings of something like

00:55:18.880 --> 00:55:22.760
that are fixing to happen—boxes,

00:55:23.079 --> 00:55:31.920
