00:56:08.400 --> 00:56:14.480
they were pouring it out on the earth.

00:56:11.280 --> 00:56:16.480
They were pouring this out on the earth,

00:56:14.480 --> 00:56:19.319
and then there were people in

00:56:16.480 --> 00:56:21.680
