00:56:27.040 --> 00:56:30.400
the earth, I don't know. I don't know if

00:56:28.640 --> 00:56:33.200
it was a type and shadow or a

00:56:30.400 --> 00:56:34.960
representation of what

00:56:33.200 --> 00:56:37.919
