00:57:02.960 --> 00:57:10.200
why you didn't. It was too holy; I

00:57:05.760 --> 00:57:13.920
can't tell you.

00:57:10.200 --> 00:57:16.399
But I see all this going on

00:57:13.920 --> 00:57:20.119
in heaven, and Jesus looked at me and he

00:57:16.400 --> 00:57:23.400
said, "You need to tell my people I'm

00:57:20.119 --> 00:57:26.960
coming. Tell my people I'm

00:57:23.400 --> 00:57:29.920
coming."I

00:57:26.960 --> 00:57:33.920
looked at him like, "Wow. Well, we know."But

00:57:29.920 --> 00:57:38.599
