00:57:33.920 --> 00:57:42.280
"No, you don't know. Tell my people I'm coming."And

00:57:38.599 --> 00:57:45.119
folks, this was in

00:57:42.280 --> 00:57:47.440
2014. Now we're in

00:57:45.119 --> 00:57:51.200
2021.

00:57:47.440 --> 00:57:54.400
I saw things when I

00:57:51.200 --> 00:57:58.240
was on the earth—some things

00:57:54.400 --> 00:58:01.040
that he told me I couldn't talk about, that

00:57:58.240 --> 00:58:05.160
I really would love to share, but

00:58:01.040 --> 00:58:09.279
I'm in obedience to him. I can't share timeframes or

00:58:05.160 --> 00:58:09.279
things like

00:58:09.319 --> 00:58:17.839
that. All I can tell you

00:58:12.680 --> 00:58:20.799
now is that we really are there. We

00:58:17.839 --> 00:58:23.920
really are.

00:58:20.799 --> 00:58:27.440
I hope I'm coming across

00:58:23.920 --> 00:58:30.640
strong about this because Jesus is

00:58:27.440 --> 00:58:32.440
coming and it's serious now, even more

00:58:30.640 --> 00:58:34.118
so than what you can

00:58:32.440 --> 00:58:37.079
comprehend.

00:58:34.119 --> 00:58:40.480
If you only really

00:58:37.079 --> 00:58:42.799
knew. That's all I can say. If you have

00:58:40.480 --> 00:58:45.839
loved ones that don't know Jesus Christ

00:58:42.799 --> 00:58:49.559
and you're scared to tell them

00:58:45.839 --> 00:58:52.160
about him, you're about to miss your

00:58:49.559 --> 00:58:55.079
opportunity and they could spend the

00:58:52.160 --> 00:58:57.799
rest of their lives in

00:58:55.079 --> 00:59:00.640
hell. You're running out of

00:58:57.799 --> 00:59:05.359
time. I'm just going to be really real

00:59:00.640 --> 00:59:09.118
with you; it's coming to a time now that

00:59:05.359 --> 00:59:12.558
it's over. And what I want to tell you

00:59:09.119 --> 00:59:16.280
now is right before I came back into

00:59:12.559 --> 00:59:18.520
