00:59:18.520 --> 00:59:24.880
before I come

00:59:20.599 --> 00:59:29.000
back to get you, they're going to talk

00:59:24.880 --> 00:59:32.559
about aliens a lot. It's one of the signs."This was

00:59:29.000 --> 00:59:34.559
in 2014.

00:59:32.559 --> 00:59:38.079
He said, "They're going to talk about

00:59:34.559 --> 00:59:39.319
aliens a lot, like it's going to become

00:59:38.079 --> 00:59:43.359
a big deal."And

00:59:39.319 --> 00:59:46.400
he told me, "You'll know and

00:59:43.359 --> 00:59:48.720
be watching for the great deception

00:59:46.400 --> 00:59:50.960
that's about to take place."There's

00:59:48.720 --> 00:59:55.319
going to be something take place. There

00:59:50.960 --> 00:59:59.359
is an event. You'll see. There's a great

00:59:55.319 --> 01:00:03.440
deception. It's all set up. When the

00:59:59.359 --> 01:00:05.359
lady at the beginning—the one

01:00:03.440 --> 01:00:07.240
I told you was frantic and

01:00:05.359 --> 01:00:09.759
screaming, 'the aliens are coming'—it's

01:00:07.240 --> 01:00:12.078
going to be talked about in

01:00:09.760 --> 01:00:14.440
the media all the time. It's going

01:00:12.079 --> 01:00:17.480
to start to become

01:00:14.440 --> 01:00:21.520
the

01:00:17.480 --> 01:00:25.160
norm. And it almost is; isn't it

01:00:21.520 --> 01:00:27.599
interesting where we are from 2014 to

01:00:25.160 --> 01:00:30.799
2021? The government is talking about it.

01:00:27.599 --> 01:00:32.119
It's almost becoming taboo, right?

01:00:30.799 --> 01:00:36.799
I mean,

01:00:32.119 --> 01:00:39.440
hello. I tried to tell people about

01:00:36.799 --> 01:00:41.359
this in 2014, and most people thought,

01:00:39.440 --> 01:00:43.520
'Oh, yeah, right. Aliens.'I

01:00:41.359 --> 01:00:45.359
said, 'Yeah, for real. That's

